813
00:50:19,809 --> 00:50:22,018
You can come here, work out,
use the equipment.

814
00:50:22,103 --> 00:50:25,188
But nobody gets in that ring
unless they're being trained.

815
00:50:25,272 --> 00:50:27,273
You wanna be trained?

816
00:50:28,484 --> 00:50:30,193
I've been watching you hit that bag.

817
00:50:30,444 --> 00:50:34,364
You got a natural right hand,
the way you throw it, the way you land it.

818
00:50:34,448 --> 00:50:36,991
Now, if I was to train you,
we'd have to start with floor work.

819
00:50:37,076 --> 00:50:41,705
'Cause see, if you don't know how to move,
you ain't got no business being in that ring.

820
00:50:41,789 --> 00:50:43,456
So what you think?

821
00:50:43,541 --> 00:50:45,458
I'd train you myself, personally.

822
00:50:48,671 --> 00:50:52,048
Nah, really, I just wanna keep doing
what I been doing.

823
00:50:52,133 --> 00:50:53,508
All right.

824
00:51:00,141 --> 00:51:02,392
Let's see that right. Uh-huh.

825
00:51:16,323 --> 00:51:18,116
Is Dukie here?

826
00:51:18,200 --> 00:51:20,994
What's that? That's for Duquan, right?

827
00:51:21,078 --> 00:51:22,704
I take it to him.

828
00:51:23,706 --> 00:51:25,123
